Title: Rent Uncollected
Plot: When Baze tells his parents about Lux, they insist in making a family dinner to meet her and Cate. Cate reluctantly agrees to go, but is annoyed when her mother and sister show up. Meanwhile, Cate hears about a gang fight at Lux's school and decides to transfer Lux to her and Baze's alma mater, Westmonte.
ParentalRatingReason: Lightbox Provisional Classification. Official NZ Rating To Be Confirmed.
